translationBlock.key: Creates a world with the specified options. If a world by that name already exists, it will instead be loaded from disk, and the last three arguments may be ignored. The name is the name of the world, type is one of NORMAL, FLAT, VERSION_1_1, LARGE_BIOMES, AMPLIFIED, CUSTOMIZED, BUFFET and environment is one of NORMAL, NETHER, THE_END. The seed can be an integer, a string (will be the hashcode), or %s (will be random int). Generator is the name of a world generator loaded on the server.
